 <body>
  <p>In Adobe Campaign, you can use the Points of Interest data collected from your mobile application's subscribers to send them personalized marketing messages, such as an email.</p> 
  <p>You can only react on Point of Interest data with standard deliveries. <a href="../../channels/using/about-transactional-messaging.md">Transactional messages</a> cannot use location data.</p> 
  <p>The earliest you can react is about 10 minutes.</p> 
  <p>In this case, you decide to send an email to all subscribers who have visited your Boston store within the last two weeks.</p> 
  <ol>
   <li><p>Create an email marketing activity.</p> </li>
   <li><p>When defining the delivery's audience, drag and drop the <strong>Subscriptions to an application</strong> element into the workspace.</p> <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/POI_subscriptions_app.png" title="" /><p>Managing audiences is detailed in the <a href="../../audiences/using/creating-audiences.md">Defining audiences</a> section.</p> </li>
   <li><p>In the <strong>Add a rule - Profile/Subscriptions to an application</strong> window, drag and drop the <strong>POI Location Subscription</strong> element into the workspace.</p> <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/POI_add_rule_profile_subscription.png" title="" /></li>
   <li><p>In the <strong>Add a rule - POI Location Subscription</strong> window, enter the label of the Point of Interest that you want to use.</p> <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/POI_location_subscription.png" title="" /></li>
   <li><p>In the <strong>Filter type</strong> field, select <strong>Relative</strong>.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Check the <strong>Preceding days</strong> option and enter <strong>15</strong> in the corresponding field.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Define the number of times the user must have visited the Point of Interest.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Click <strong>Confirm</strong> to save your audience.</p> <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/POI_subscriptions_app_audience_defined.png" title="" /></li>
   <li><p>Add content to your email.</p> <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/POI_email_content.png" title="" /></li>
   <li><p>Confirm creating the activity to view the email's dashboard.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Send your message. </p> </li>
  </ol>
  <p>The email with the 10% discount offer will be sent to subscribers who:</p> 
  <ul>
   <li><p>Visited your Boston store at least once within the last two weeks.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Had your mobile application in the foreground at least once during the visit.</p> </li>
  </ul>
